Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.79,0:00:14.84,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\blur1\pos(463.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.15,0:00:15.74,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.74,0:00:19.27,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.27,0:00:22.96,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.96,0:00:26.58,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.58,0:00:30.34,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.34,0:00:33.51,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.88,0:00:36.64,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.64,0:00:40.10,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.18,0:00:44.77,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.77,0:00:48.27,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.27,0:00:51.07,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:54.49,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.66,0:00:59.28,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.28,0:01:02.62,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.09,0:01:11.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.76,0:01:13.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.96,0:01:15.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:19.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.78,0:01:23.67,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HFCFFFE&\b1\pos(495.495,286.833)}The Reborn Cobra Man
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.50,0:01:39.65,Sign,,0,0,20,,{\an7\fs55\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&}We Buy Dogs and Cats Ayakoji\NBiological Research Facility
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.52,0:01:44.96,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs60\3c&H4D5556&\c&H12130D&}Ayakoji Biological\NResearch Facility
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.62,0:01:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Right this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.76,0:02:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.04,0:02:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.75,0:02:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, please. Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.73,0:02:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, we can prepare the\Nanimal blood to revive Cobra Man,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.67,0:02:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,while choosing the best of the\Nhumans to become combatants.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.39,0:03:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Cobra Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I will restore the body that\Nwas damaged by Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.89,0:03:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Cobra Man targeted the Ministry\Nof Finance's gold reserves,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.78,0:03:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,but failed due to the\NKamen Rider's interference.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.33,0:03:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Cobra Man,\Ninjured by the Kamen Rider,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.75,0:03:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,was about to receive surgery that\Nwould bring him back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.25,0:03:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll pay soon, Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.09,0:03:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.55,0:03:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Toru's dog went missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.74,0:03:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.76,0:03:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that reminds me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.61,0:03:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a place that's paying\Na lot of money for dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.97,0:03:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,One of our customers\Nmentioned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.74,0:04:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You think someone stole\NToru's dog to sell it to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.05,0:04:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If they did...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.33,0:04:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so sad for Toru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.13,0:04:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.49,0:04:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The place
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.32,0:04:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,buying dogs is the Ayakoji\NBiological Research Facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.16,0:04:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen the signs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.33,0:04:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayakoji Research Facility?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.42,0:04:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you crying about, Toru?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.64,0:04:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Toru.\NI'll buy you a treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.52,0:04:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Toru's such a good kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.42,0:04:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... with his mother gone,\Nit can be hard to keep up with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.47,0:04:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to work on\NSundays, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.66,0:04:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.54,0:04:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I'm afraid detectives\Ndon't get days off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.38,0:04:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And with a new rash of\Nmysterious disappearances,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.90,0:04:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even have time to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.25,0:04:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mysterious disappearances?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.12,0:04:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:58.28,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an9\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}We're no longer\Nbuying dogs and cats
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:05:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess this is the place\Nthat's buying dogs...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.80,0:05:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right...\Nmaybe my dog is here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.65,0:05:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Toru, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.85,0:05:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad,\NI think Taro might be in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.28,0:05:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If he is, I'll bring him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.23,0:05:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.94,0:05:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.88,0:05:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Toru, have I ever lied to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.52,0:05:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.46,0:05:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. I'm with the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to talk to\Nwhoever's in charge here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.64,0:05:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.48,0:06:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait here, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.80,0:06:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone who disappeared sold\Nan animal to this facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.01,0:06:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something more\Nto this laboratory...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.24,0:07:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Rise, Cobra Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.75,0:07:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You are restored.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.40,0:07:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Cobra Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.21,0:07:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I have brought you back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.93,0:07:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You died in your fight\Nwith Kamen Rider,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,but I have breathed your\Ndevil's life back into you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, rise!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.32,0:07:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Rise, and fight Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.65,0:07:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.04,0:07:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on Cobra\NMan's successful surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Just today, a large amount of gold bullion
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.80,0:07:48.53,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\3c&H323D34&\c&HA4CFE4&\bord4}Ministry of Finance
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,was transmitted from all over\NJapan to the Japan Gold Repository.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.18,0:07:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A few days from now,\Na ship called the President will arrive in
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.33,0:08:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yokohama Harbor and\Ntake that gold away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.18,0:08:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's valued at billions of yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.93,0:08:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You must steal that gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.46,0:08:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If you fail,\Nyou will pay for it with your lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.76,0:08:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the law of Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.10,0:08:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I pray for your success.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.90,0:08:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad's been gone a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.79,0:08:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.33,0:08:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.05,0:08:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying you saw a monster\Nat Ayakoji Research Facility?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.23,0:08:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.60,0:08:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it ate my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.63,0:09:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Could Shocker have\Ncreated a new cyborg?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.13,0:09:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Mr. Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi.\NWhat'll it be? Coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.56,0:09:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi, perfect timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.74,0:09:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, begin the experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.04,0:09:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.00,0:09:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Cobra Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.44,0:09:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,These men are garbage,\Nunfit to become Shocker combatants.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.65,0:09:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They're perfect test\Nsubjects for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.11,0:09:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And to test your\Npower, as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.04,0:09:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You came right to us, Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.06,0:10:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Now die,\Nto test Cobra Man's power!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.70,0:10:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew Shocker was\Ninvolved in this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.53,0:10:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.24,0:10:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Cobra Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.60,0:10:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin the test!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.15,0:10:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, don't kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.81,0:10:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The experiment is successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.28,0:11:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Who... Who are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.45,0:11:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, talk!\NWhere is Detective Koga?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.72,0:11:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,In... the forest around back...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.91,0:11:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:48.22,Bumper Episode 2-13,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\pos(345,530)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.78,0:11:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, this man!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.91,0:12:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... don't do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.09,0:12:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Fix your aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.33,0:12:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.30,0:12:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Cobra Man... you're alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.34,0:12:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.81,0:12:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker's power knows no limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.91,0:12:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I will perform\Nthe surgery on your brain...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And I will bring you\Ninto Shocker's fold!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.66,0:13:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Burn the Rider to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.03,0:14:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Koga!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.26,0:14:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Koga!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.55,0:14:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mr. Koga!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.65,0:14:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The culprit...\Nwhere did the culprit go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Koga... you can't pursue\Na culprit in your condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.80,0:14:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.97,0:14:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.31,0:14:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on,\Nlet's get you to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.92,0:14:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I must capture the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.52,0:14:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Koga! Mr. Koga, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.69,0:14:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Koga!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.67,0:14:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief.\NWhat a difficult detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at my face!\NThis is all your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.27,0:15:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.59,0:15:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, you wretch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.49,0:15:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.23,0:15:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.99,0:15:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko Ayakoji...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.83,0:15:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Your usefulness is at an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.68,0:15:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.89,0:15:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I was merely using your skills\Nto bring Cobra Man back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.88,0:15:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You tricked me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.06,0:15:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.90,0:15:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's too late\Nto save you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.96,0:15:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Cobra Man, kill that woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Cobra Man, the President has\Narrived in the Port of Yokohama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The gold will be brought there tomorrow\Nfrom the Japanese Gold Repository.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Attack it, as we planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.55,0:16:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.95,0:16:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Koga went to\Nthe gold repository?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.72,0:16:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NWe tried to stop him, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.41,0:16:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Toru said that some gold\Nwas being transferred today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.97,0:16:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bet you Shocker\Nrevived Cobra Man
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.70,0:16:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,to get at that gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.35,0:16:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi, you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.25,0:16:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I'll let\NShocker get away with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.37,0:16:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.91,0:16:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything out of the ordinary?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.78,0:16:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.60,0:16:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Koga.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.15,0:17:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't have a repeat of last\Ntime, will we?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.56,0:17:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We have police stationed\Nalong the route,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.57,0:17:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and the President in\Nthe Port of Yokohama has
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.26,0:17:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,been cordoned off,\Nwith lots of security.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.73,0:17:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Koga.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there, Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.48,0:17:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I have a word, Mr. Koga?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.25,0:17:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.07,0:17:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.39,0:17:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Koga.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.72,0:17:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker is after this gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You should call\Noff the transfer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.04,0:17:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.30,0:17:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.48,0:17:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A secret organization\Nbent on world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.67,0:17:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo, what in the world\Nare you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.22,0:17:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Our department hasn't\Nheard anything about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.49,0:17:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.30,0:17:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Look... even if an organization\Nlike that did exist,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.10,0:17:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the Japanese government won't be\Ncowed by some petty band of thieves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.14,0:18:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If we canceled the transfer, the Japanese\Npolice would become a laughingstock.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.70,0:18:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave this to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.86,0:18:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody knows about\NShocker's existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Fighting Shocker by myself\Nis the only path I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.14,0:18:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,With security like this,\Nnobody can interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.37,0:18:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.37,0:18:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,On the honor of the Tokyo Police\NDepartment, I'll get that gold to Yokohama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.56,0:18:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,When, where,\Nand how will Shocker attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.21,0:19:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it.\NNo sign of this 'Shocker' at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.79,0:19:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo must enjoy scaring people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.95,0:19:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Mr. Koga?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.24,0:19:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talking to yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.62,0:19:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I was just saying that\Nthe mission's going smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.99,0:19:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.42,0:19:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that's broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.15,0:20:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.16,0:20:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.45,0:20:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider! Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.08,0:21:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.31,0:22:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Throw!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.13,0:22:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.35,0:22:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad got a commendation\Nfrom the commissioner.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.97,0:22:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you don't need to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.94,0:22:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.07,0:22:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,My, my, a commendation!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.14,0:22:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.20,0:22:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Right this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.85,0:22:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A coffee for Mr. Koga.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.85,0:22:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.42,0:22:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker never showed\Nup in the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.48,0:22:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But I just can't figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.93,0:23:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Who got the bullion\Noff the boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.57,0:23:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I assumed it was you, Mr. Koga.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.46,0:23:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.77,0:23:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I got knocked out by\Nthe boat explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.60,0:23:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's tell everyone it was\Nme, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.34,0:23:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, you couldn't\Ndo something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.86,0:23:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But who could it have been?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.87,0:23:29.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi saved Japan from\NShocker's evil once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.01,0:23:32.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Will he ever get to be\Na normal human again?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.99,0:23:40.59,Cont,,570,0,140,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.83,0:23:43.10,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(502.031,486.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.12,0:23:46.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.36,0:23:48.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is Gebacondor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.38,0:23:51.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He drinks the blood of young women and\Nhe exceeds Rider in destructive power.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.95,0:23:54.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,One by one, white wedding\Ndresses are stained in blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.42,0:23:57.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week\Nfor more Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.25,0:24:00.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in "Blood-Sucking\NMonster Gebacondor."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.88,0:24:10.72,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.30,0:24:13.30,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.30,0:24:15.26,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.26,0:24:18.31,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.81,0:24:20.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.69,0:24:22.56,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.56,0:24:24.36,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.36,0:24:25.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.15,0:24:28.19,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.24,0:24:33.91,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.91,0:24:37.49,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.49,0:24:41.08,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.58,0:24:45.34,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!